fg
\int_{0}^Tf(x)g(x)dx.
(fg)_n(x):=\sum_{i=1}^{n}\chi_{[t_i,t_{i+1})}(x)(fg)(t_i)
\int_0^T(fg)_n(x)dx=\frac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^nf(t_i)g(t_i).
[0,T]
\varepsilon>0
n
|t_{i+1}-t_i|\leq \frac{1}{n}
|(fg)(t_{i+1})-(fg)(t_i)|< \frac{\varepsilon}{T}
\int_0^T|(fg)_n(x)-(fg)(x)|dx\leq\int_0^T\frac{\varepsilon}{T}dx=\varepsilon
